						<div class="about_r">
				<div class="h4">Why Wellav?</div>
				<div class="p">Wellav, the gateway to better video delivery, is a leading provider of video delivery solutions for broadcaster, pay-tv and enterprise IPTV system. Under two business centers (USA and China) with sales and support teams around the world, Wellav fully integrated R&amp;D, manufacturing, distribution and marketing.We continue to meet the needs of modern media with a cutting-edge product portfolio.</div>
				<a href="/company-wellav-sencore_d20" class="my_more1">view more</a>
