<div class="pro_section clearfix">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="i_title">
			<div class="h4">HOT PRODUCTS</div>
			<span class="animate-border ml-auto mr-auto tw-mt-20"></span>
		</div>
		<div class="button_outside">
			<div class="swiper-container swi_overflow pro_scrollbar">
				<ul class="swiper-wrapper">
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/cmp200_p13.html" title="CMP200" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="Modular video processing platform" src="/uploadfile/202308/18/213d396f576ce0254f25a216b01e1300_medium.jpg" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/cmp200_p13.html" title="CMP200">CMP200</a></div>
						<p>CMP200 is a next-gen modular video processor from Wellav. It balances performance &amp; cost for multi-channel encoding, HD transcoding, IPTV+QAM distribution, with global support &amp; intuitive web UI. Featuring dual power options, 6 hot-swappable modules, IP switch, it is ideal for hospitality, e...</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/umh160r_p19.html" title="UMH160R" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="SD/HD Receiver/Decoder" src="/uploadfile/202305/19/3d01312d39ee6331826f9d344b875d7d_medium.png" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/umh160r_p19.html" title="UMH160R">UMH160R</a></div>
						<p>UMH160R is a powerful and cost-effective broadcast level decoder. It supports signal receiving, multi-channel descrambling and external table/data insertion. It also supports MPEG2/MPEG4 SD/HD program decoding with two audio channels. With a remote, web-based management interface, it is ideal to sup...</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/cmp100_p9.html" title="CMP100" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="Modular video processing platform" src="/uploadfile/202305/19/f3649995900608ce1adbf46f82901f88_medium.jpg" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/cmp100_p9.html" title="CMP100">CMP100</a></div>
						<p>The most powerful video headend packed in 4 RU! Perfect for hotels, schools, hospitals, and MDUs yet fexible and feature rich to meet the needs of professional and commercial CATV and IPTV systems.&nbsp;</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/dmp900_p14.html" title="DMP900" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="Digital Media Platform" src="/uploadfile/202305/19/20bdf596dcb4ff440ab20e695ec56b05_medium.jpg" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/dmp900_p14.html" title="DMP900">DMP900</a></div>
						<p>DMP900 is Wellav&rsquo;s most advanced product for service operators. It provides proven headend technology in a compact, 1RU chassis. With wide variety of different input and output module options that can be combined as needed, it offers a true, comprehensive video delivery solution.</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/impulse-300d_p15.html" title="Impulse 300D" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="Network Decoder" src="/uploadfile/202305/19/6d5825487356ab6f6a44b5d07e829470_medium.jpg" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/impulse-300d_p15.html" title="Impulse 300D">Impulse 300D</a></div>
						<p>The Impulse 300D is a dynamic approach to the single channel decoder concept, supporting content reception from traditional multicast and OTT sources with SDI, HDMI, and analog outputs. Equipped with 4K/UHD capability via HDMI, it doubles as a standalone solution or rack-mountable triple-unit setup ...</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/omp150_p16.html" title="OMP150" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="IPTV System" src="/uploadfile/202305/19/a2fffe8419c787ae31e905e90e4dd85a_medium.jpg" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/omp150_p16.html" title="OMP150">OMP150</a></div>
						<p>The OMP150 IPTV system offers a user-friendly yet powerful solution for centralized management of Android-based set-top boxes. As IPTV technology gains traction, it is ideal for hospitality, education, government, and other facilities needing to stream IP videos across multiple TVs. &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/audio-control-management-host_p39.html" title="Audio Control Management Host" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="Audio Control Management Host" src="/uploadfile/202501/06/831d83fd036d24f8d4730453a6d9a087_medium.jpg" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/audio-control-management-host_p39.html" title="Audio Control Management Host">Audio Control Management Host</a></div>
						<p>ACP-HW-7U &nbsp; As the core management device of the audio control system, the host is deployed in the master control room to enable centralized management of all IP terminals across the system. It allows full control over audio sources and custom paging zone grouping. Housed in an industrial-grade...</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
								<li class="swiper-slide">
				  <div class="li clearfix">
					<a href="/paging-console_p41.html" title="Paging Console" class="img"><img id="product_detail_img"  alt="Paging Console" src="/uploadfile/202501/06/0268c44b46965bb610b177e26ddce398_medium.jpg" /></a>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="h4"><a href="/paging-console_p41.html" title="Paging Console">Paging Console</a></div>
						<p>PAG-01 &nbsp; The paging console is typically deployed on the desk in a broadcasting room. It connects and communicates via IP network with the broadcasting host, enabling quick zone and group selection for microphone or file-based broadcasting.</p>
					</div>
				 </div>
				</li>
				  
			  </ul>
